def saveToFile(self):
        try:
            f = open(self.dirname + '/protoPaletteData.py', 'w')
            f.write("from direct.leveleditor.ObjectPaletteBase import *\n\n")
            f.write("protoData = {\n")
            self.saveProtoData(f)
            f.write("}\n")
            f.write("protoDataStruct = {\n")
            self.saveProtoDataStruct(f)
            f.write("}\n")
            f.close()
        except:
            pass
